 <name>fnbind</name>
 <channel>pecl.php.net</channel>
 <summary>Allows you to define a function from a closure.</summary>
 <description>class Bar {
  function quux() { echo "Hello world!\n"; }
}
  $bar = new Bar(); $bar->quux(...);
  fnbind_add_closure('foo', $bar->quux(...));
 </description>
